ch.bfh.bti7301.hs2013.gravis.core

Class CoreFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.bfh.bti7301.hs2013.gravis.core.CoreFactory

  • public final class CoreFactory
extends Object
    This factory class creates and composes all necessary objects used in the gravis core package. The construction of objects is centralized in this class. All necessary dependencies are passed through the constructors and methods to the objects (dependency injection). An object speaks only through an interface to other dependant objects.
    Author:
    Patrick Kofmel (kofmp1@bfh.ch), Roland Bruggmann (brugr9@bfh.ch)
